ONE-TIME:
git remote add upstream https://github.com/ORIGINAL_OWNER/ORIGINAL_REPOSITORY.git

ONCE DONE:
BEFORE BEGINNING WORK, BRING FORK UP TO DATE
git fetch upstream
git checkout master
git merge upstream/master
git branch mybranchname
git checkout mybranchname (n.b. your work should be in mybranchname)

DO UR WORK, BRING IN UR CHANGES
git add .
git commit -m 'commit message'
git push origin mybranchname

THEN SUBMIT THE PULL REQUEST ON GITHUB.
